embeds.title: Welcome [USER]
embeds.description:
Thank you for reaching out for a pixel art builder!

To get started, simply complete this form:
```
1. Your Discord Name
2. Roblox Username
3. Island Code
4. The build you need
```
Add a **description** or **images of the build** you're envisioning if possible.

We're excited to bring your pixel art dreams to life!
